269
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:08,602
Rym: I don't either.

270
00:14:08,642 --> 00:14:12,279
Scott: But so far, the only thing I've heard about that is you telling me when I got home.

271
00:14:12,681 --> 00:14:13,886
Rym: Actually, it was all over the news.

272
00:14:14,047 --> 00:14:14,469
Rym: Yeah.

273
00:14:14,609 --> 00:14:18,261
