274
00:14:18,281 --> 00:14:26,552
Rym: I guess it bothers me whenever someone goes on the Internet and sees something that offends them or that is in violation of their local laws.

275
00:14:26,954 --> 00:14:39,982
Rym: And they somehow feel that because it has affected them, that they have the right to tell the rest of the world who doesn't believe in their bullshit, doesn't have any law making it illegal to do this thing and doesn't care what to do.

276
00:14:40,002 --> 00:14:50,718
Rym: If I want to draw a picture of Mohammed hugging the king of Thailand next to a giant foot, I am perfectly OK with doing that because I'm not a Muslim and I'm not a citizen of Thailand.

277
00:14:50,979 --> 00:14:53,989
Scott: I mean, laws are all about social contract.

278
00:14:54,009 --> 00:15:01,538
Scott: You know, people agree with each other to do certain things, you know, and not to do certain things, because that's what the society is agreed upon.

279
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:08,002
Scott: If some other society of people agrees upon something, well, they can all follow whatever they agreed upon.

280
00:15:08,083 --> 00:15:10,973
Scott: And us people over here follow what we agreed upon.

281
00:15:11,535 --> 00:15:18,639
Scott: And if something that we do happens to fly over and bump into your society and you don't like it, tough shit.

282
00:15:18,980 --> 00:15:24,057
Scott: If you do something that happens to fly over and bump into us, tough shit for us to now.

283
00:15:24,097 --> 00:15:36,840
Rym: granted not to say that I am in any way saying that cultural relativism is something we should strive for, because there are a lot of things that offend me out there in the world that people do in certain countries.

284
00:15:37,262 --> 00:15:42,749
Rym: And at the same time, I feel very justified in being offended by those things and doing everything in my power to end those things.

285
00:15:43,330 --> 00:15:57,372
Rym: But if something is media, just media, and it is put on to Internet, you know, that giant Wild West of Bhutanari girls running around hitting people in the foot with Thai one of these kings.

286
00:15:58,236 --> 00:15:59,480
Rym: There's nothing wrong with that.

287
00:15:59,561 --> 00:16:02,231
