Rym: Does it look like it's easy to take apart?

835
00:49:13,698 --> 00:49:15,445
Rym: Does it look like the cages come out?

836
00:49:15,787 --> 00:49:16,530
Rym: Look at the reviews.

837
00:49:16,870 --> 00:49:18,817
Rym: People who have problems will tell you they have problems.

838
00:49:18,877 --> 00:49:19,941
Rym: Believe me, they will.

839
00:49:19,961 --> 00:49:25,483
Scott: Yep, so computer case, perhaps one of the most important parts of the computer.

